\section{Objectives and Scope}\label{Objectives_thesis}
Following the survey of various available published literatures we propose
\begin{enumerate}[(i)]
\item to reconsider the H-plane horn radiation problem using GTD with spherical source
incidence.
\item to obtain a finite edge GTD formulation using available corner diffraction coefficient.
\item to present a new corner slope diffraction (CSD) coefficient and its heuristic derivation.
\item in addition to carry out FDTD analysis of the H-plane horn radiation problem.
\item to obtain a comprehensive finite edge GTD formulation of the H-plane horn radiation problem using available corner diffraction coefficient and the new CSD and compare with FDTD predictions and also results available in open literature.
\item to consider several antennas in receiving mode. Specifically to carry out the performance analysis of wire, microstrip and aperture antennas as EMFS using the FDTD technique.
\item to present some empirical formulas for quick calculation of AFs.
\end{enumerate}
